OL,3,CEluned Morgan set to become First
OL,4,CMinister and inherit toughest task in
OL,5,C25 years
OL,7,FEluned Morgan is set to be confirmed
OL,8,Fas the next First Minister of Wales,
OL,9,Fand the first woman to fill the role,
OL,10,Fin a special meeting of the Senedd on
OL,11,FTuesday, 6 August.
OL,13,FThe current health secretary became
OL,14,Fleader of Welsh Labour on 24 July
OL,15,Fafter no other candidate came forward
OL,16,Fin the leadership election to replace
OL,17,FVaughan Gething.
