OL,3,CEluned Morgan set to become First
OL,4,CMinister and inherit toughest task in
OL,5,C25 years
OL,7,FHe said he would resign just four
OL,8,Fmonths after taking the top job,
OL,9,Ffollowing an intense period of
OL,10,Fcontroversy and criticism including
OL,11,Fover donations to his leadership
OL,12,Fcampaign and the sacking of a cabinet
OL,13,Fminister.
OL,15,FWhat will happen today?
OL,17,FWhat will happen on Tuesday is the
OL,18,Fformal process of choosing a first
OL,19,Fminister and Senedd members are being
OL,20,Frecalled from their summer recess to
OL,21,Fcarry out that process.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/16
