OL,3,CEluned Morgan set to become First
OL,4,CMinister and inherit toughest task in
OL,5,C25 years
OL,7,FIt is the first time the Welsh
OL,8,FParliament has been recalled for that
OL,9,Fpurpose since devolution began in
OL,10,F1999. Previous recalls have been to
OL,11,Fdiscuss pressing matters like the
OL,12,FCovid pandemic, Brexit and the future
OL,13,Fof the steel industry.
OL,15,FThe last time it was recalled was in
OL,16,FSeptember 2022 to pay tribute
OL,17,Ffollowing the death of HM Queen
OL,18,FElizabeth II.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/16
