OL,3,CEluned Morgan set to become First
OL,4,CMinister and inherit toughest task in
OL,5,C25 years
OL,7,FThis time, it is meeting in what is
OL,8,Fknown as hybrid form, meaning that
OL,9,Fsome members will be in the chamber in
OL,10,FCardiff Bay while others will attend
OL,11,Fand vote virtually.
OL,13,FArrangements have also been made to
OL,14,Fallow MSs who are overseas to play
OL,15,Ftheir part. Previously that wasn't
OL,16,Fallowed.
OL,18,FVoting is done via a 'roll call' in
OL,19,Fwhich Senedd members are called in
OL,20,Falphabetical order to say who they
OL,21,Fwant to be first minister.
