OL,3,CEluned Morgan set to become First
OL,4,CMinister and inherit toughest task in
OL,5,C25 years
OL,7,FLabour members are expected to
OL,8,Fnominate Eluned Morgan while the
OL,9,FConservatives and Plaid Cymru will
OL,10,Fnominate their own leaders.
OL,12,FLabour is the largest party in the
OL,13,FSenedd but doesn't have a majority so
OL,14,Fif all three opposition parties join
OL,15,Fforces they could block Eluned
OL,16,FMorgan's nomination.
OL,18,FHowever, Liberal Democrat leader Jane
OL,19,FDodds is expected to abstain, meaning
OL,20,FMs Morgan is almost certain to be
OL,21,Fchosen.
