OL,7,FOnce that decision has been taken, the
OL,8,FLlywydd or Presiding Officer, Elin
OL,9,FJones, will contact the King to inform
OL,10,Fhim of the Senedd's choice.
OL,12,FAt some point during the afternoon,
OL,13,Fthe King will confirm he has appointed
OL,14,FEluned Morgan to be first minister
OL,15,Fafter which she will swear her oath of
OL,16,Foffice in front of a judge.
OL,18,FAfter that, the hard work begins.
