OL,3,CEluned Morgan set to become First
OL,4,CMinister and inherit toughest task in
OL,5,C25 years
OL,7,FHer first task will be to appoint a
OL,8,Fcabinet. Given how deeply divided the
OL,9,FLabour group has been in the last few
OL,10,Fmonths, that won't be an easy job.
OL,12,FShould she appoint her predecessor
OL,13,FVaughan Gething or does she need to
OL,14,Fput further distance between her time
OL,15,Fin charge and the divisive period of
OL,16,Fhis time?
OL,18,FWho will take over from Eluned Morgan
OL,19,Fin health? There's speculation that
OL,20,Fthe former economy secretary, Jeremy
OL,21,FMiles, will be given the job.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/16
