OL,7,FHe stood in the leadership election
OL,8,Fwhich Vaughan Gething won but decided
OL,9,Fnot to stand this time in the
OL,10,Finterests of party unity.
OL,12,FFor many Gething supporters, Mr Miles
OL,13,Fis seen as being part of the problems
OL,14,Fwhich engulfed their party this year,
OL,15,Fwhich could lead to problems further
OL,16,Fdown the line.
