OL,3,CEluned Morgan set to become First
OL,4,CMinister and inherit toughest task in
OL,5,C25 years
OL,7,FI'm told that the Labour group is
OL,8,Fdetermined to put aside its
OL,9,Fdifferences and heal its wounds, but
OL,10,Fthose wounds are deep and healing them
OL,11,Fwon't be easy.
OL,13,FNot only that but the new first
OL,14,Fminister will need to reach out to
OL,15,Fother parties because Labour's lack of
OL,16,Fmajority means it will need the
OL,17,Fsupport or abstention of at least one
OL,18,Fof the opposition groups (including
OL,19,Fthe single Lib Dem MS) to pass
OL,20,Flegislation and, more crucially, its
OL,21,Fbudget.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/16
