OL,3,CEluned Morgan set to become First
OL,4,CMinister and inherit toughest task in
OL,5,C25 years
OL,7,FThat had become an impossibility under
OL,8,FVaughan Gething because all opposition
OL,9,Fmembers had voted against him in a
OL,10,Fconfidence vote, making it unlikely
OL,11,Fthat any deal could change their mind.
OL,13,FEluned Morgan will have to start talks
OL,14,Fstraight away if they haven't already
OL,15,Fbegun with the Conservatives, Plaid
OL,16,FCymru and the Lib Dems, to see what
OL,17,Fwould persuade them to allow her
OL,18,Fbudget to pass at the end of the year.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/16
