OL,3,CEluned Morgan set to become First
OL,4,CMinister and inherit toughest task in
OL,5,C25 years
OL,7,FIf she can't do that, then we really
OL,8,Fare in uncharted waters. If a first
OL,9,Fminister can't govern, it could lead
OL,10,Fto an early Senedd election when the
OL,11,Fnext one isn't due to be held until
OL,12,F2026.
OL,14,FThat's certainly what Plaid Cymru is
OL,15,Fcalling for, pointing out that Labour
OL,16,Fpoliticians regularly called for a UK
OL,17,Felection when the Conservatives had
OL,18,Fthree prime ministers in one year
OL,19,Fwithout an election.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/16
