OL,4,CMinister and inherit toughest task in
OL,5,C25 years
OL,7,FNow that there have been three first
OL,8,Fministers in one year, Plaid Cymru
OL,9,Fargues that voters here in Wales
OL,10,Fshould be given a say. It's a view
OL,11,Fthat has been shared by some within
OL,12,FWelsh Labour, too, though I detect
OL,13,Fthat the appetite for that may have
OL,14,Fgone away.
OL,16,FEarly or not, an election is very much
OL,17,Fon Labour's minds.
