OL,7,FMany within the party here in Wales
OL,8,Fthink they are on course for a
OL,9,Fhammering in 2026, something borne out
OL,10,Fby recent research from Cardiff
OL,11,FUniversity's Wales Governance Centre,
OL,12,Fa hammering likely to be made worse by
OL,13,Fa new, proportional voting system
OL,14,Fwhich Labour itself (with the support
OL,15,Fof Plaid Cymru) is introducing.
