OL,3,CEluned Morgan set to become First
OL,4,CMinister and inherit toughest task in
OL,5,C25 years
OL,7,FSo, in a short space of time, Eluned
OL,8,FMorgan has to unite the divided Labour
OL,9,Fgroup in the Senedd, reach deals with
OL,10,Fopposition parties that will enable
OL,11,Fher to get a budget and future
OL,12,Flegislation as well as persuading
OL,13,Fvoters to give her party another
OL,14,Fchance in 2026 at a time when funding
OL,15,Fis shrinking and the ability to blame
OL,16,FConservative UK governments has
OL,17,Fdisappeared.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/16
