OL,3,CEluned Morgan set to become First
OL,4,CMinister and inherit toughest task in
OL,5,C25 years
OL,7,FAll of that means that she's about to
OL,8,Fhave the most difficult task of any FM
OL,9,Fin 25 years, but one thing that might
OL,10,Fhelp her is her own experience in
OL,11,Fpolitics.
OL,13,FIt may sound strange to describe
OL,14,Fanyone who's a Baroness and has been
OL,15,Fin elected Labour politics for 30
OL,16,Fyears as an underdog, but in some ways
OL,17,Fshe has been just that.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/16
