OL,3,CEluned Morgan set to become First
OL,4,CMinister and inherit toughest task in
OL,5,C25 years
OL,7,FShe has been seen as too 'Blairite'
OL,8,Ffor many on the left in Welsh Labour
OL,9,Fand too left-wing for many in the
OL,10,Fcentre. She nearly didn't make it to
OL,11,Fthe ballot in 2018's leadership
OL,12,Felection, only Carwyn Jones 'lending'
OL,13,Fhis nomination to ensure a woman was
OL,14,Fin the contest enabled her to stand.
OL,16,FNow with the odds so heavily stacked
OL,17,Fagainst her, as well as being the
OL,18,Ffirst female first minister, she could
OL,19,Falso be the first underdog first
OL,20,Fminister.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/16
